Name: Every Flavor Bell Crab
AttributesDescription: Increases ATK and Crit. Rate of all Resonators in the team by 22% and 12% respectively for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
BgDescription: The troupe's favorite seafood, Bell Crab, is the soul of this dish. Each Bell Crab finds its perfect shell, giving it a distinct flavor. Before every meal, the troupe members place a bet: What will the next crab taste like?
